                    <outline text="Security Management and Assessment Taxonomy">
                        <outline text="When assessing the security of an organisation, security management and assessment are vital techniques to achieve confidentiality, integrity and availability of key assets. A great number of different frameworks have been suggested in the literature, and in this project you will give an overview and critical analysis and comparison of the individual methodologies. An additional contribution would be the application of a particular method to a real (or fictitious) scenario."/>
